short.ar: بنقرة واحدة يمكنك استخراج بيانات منشورات Facebook من صفحة نتائج البحث كملف Excel/CSV/JSON/HTML/XML.
short.am: አንድ ጠቅታ የፌስቡክ ልጥፎችን ውሂብ ከፍለጋው ውጤት ገጽ እንደ Excel/CSV/JSON/HTML/XML ፋይል ማውጣት።
short.bg: Извлечете с едно щракване данни за публикации във Facebook от страницата с резултати от търсенето като Excel/CSV/JSON/HTML/XML файл.
short.bn: এক্সেল/CSV/JSON/HTML/XML ফাইল হিসাবে অনুসন্ধান ফলাফল পৃষ্ঠা থেকে এক-ক্লিক Facebook পোস্টের ডেটা বের করুন।

short.en,en_AU,en_GB,en_US,es_419,pt_BR,pt_PT,: One-click extract Substack Publication data from the search result page as Excel/CSV/JSON/HTML/XML file.
short.es: Con un solo clic, extraiga los datos de las publicaciones de Facebook de la página de resultados de búsqueda como un archivo…

short.he: חילוץ בלחיצה אחת פייסבוק מפרסמת נתונים מדף תוצאות החיפוש כקובץ Excel/CSV/JSON/HTML/XML.
short.hi: खोज परिणाम पृष्ठ से एक्सेल/सीएसवी/जेएसओएन/एचटीएमएल/एक्सएमएल फ़ाइल के रूप में एक-क्लिक से फेसबुक पोस्ट डेटा निकालें।

short.tr: Tek tıklamayla Facebook gönderi verilerini arama sonucu sayfasından Excel/CSV/JSON/HTML/XML dosyası olarak çıkarın.

short.zh_CN: 一键从搜索结果页面提取 Facebook 帖子数据为 Excel/CSV/JSON/HTML/XML 文件。

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
🚀 Effortlessly extract substack publication data from the publication search page to a Excel/CSV/JSON/HTML/XML file.

🔧 How it Works:
1️⃣ Go to the substack publication search page.
2️⃣ Perform a search, then click the "Start" button on extension popup.
3️⃣ Choose to download from the data scraping pop-up or the task list on extension.

🌳 What groups data can I extract using this tool?
Like author_id, copyright, cover_photo_url, created_at, custom_domain, hero_image, hero_text, homepage_type, id, invite_only, language, logo_url, name, type, is_personal_mode, plans, author_name, author_handle, author_photo_url, author_bio, has_posts, has_podcast, has_free_podcast, has_subscriber_only_podcast, has_community_content, freeSubscriberCount, base_url, hostname, is_on_substack and so on.

Note: This extension is an independent creation and is not affiliated with or endorsed by substack❗️🔒
